	(rtx-true,rtx-false,rtx-canonical-bool): New procs.
	(rtx-simplify): Handle not,orif,andif.
	* semantics.scm (-simplify-for-compilation): Simplify not,orif,andif.
	* utils.scm (alist-copy): New proc.
